<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- ʿulĩqa ạl̊fādī ʿalay̱
 ʿūdi ṣal̊biⁿ wāủhīn̊
 kulã huz̊ʾiⁿ ḥamala
 wah̊wa rabũ ạl̊ʿālamīn̊

[V2]
 2- ạảẓ̊lamat̊ sẖam̊su ạlsãmā
 sẖuqĩqat̊ ṣumũ ạlṣũkẖūr̊
 sẖuqã dẖalika ạl̊ḥijāb̊
 futiḥat̊ til̊ka ạl̊qubūr̊

[V3]
 3- ạảs̊lama ạlrũwḥa wamāt̊
 ʿan̊ fujãạriⁿ wakẖuṭāh̊
 fī ẓalạmi ạl̊qab̊ri bāt̊
 wah̊wa rayỉysu ạl̊ḥayāh̊

[V4]
 4- dufina muḥ̊yī ạlrãmīm̊
 fī ḍarīḥ iⁿkāl̊basẖar̊
 wākẖ̊tafay̱ ạldũrũ ạlnãẓīm̊
 ḍim̊na makẖ̊tūmi ạl̊ḥajar̊

[V5]
 5- qāma fī ạlṣũb̊ḥi ạl̊munīr̊
 fajalạ laẙla ạldũjay̱
 mūfīaⁿạ ʿad̊la ạl̊qadīr̊
 qāhiraⁿạ jaẙsẖa ạl̊ʿiday̱

[V6]
 6- wāʿ̊talay̱ ạl̊ʿar̊sẖa ạlrãfīʿ̊
 sẖāfiʿaⁿạ fī ạl̊mū̊̉minīn̊
 falidẖā ạl̊faḍ̊la nudẖīʿ̊
 sẖākirīna kulã ḥīn̊</lyrics>
<aka>ʿlq ạlfạdy ʿly̱ ʿwd ṣlb wạ̉hyn</aka>
<title>ʿlq ạlfạdy ʿly̱</title>
<author>ywạkym msʿwd ạlrạsy</author>
